flowRoot.flowPara: This group is for windows with configurable settings, what we indetified as the second level on the user's needs.
Here we group the tools that will be used in most case scenarios.
We create 3 subgroups: Shapes, Draw lines and Fill areas. Each group contains tools which affect our work in a similar way.
Draw a square/rectangle, circle/ellipsis, polygon/star, 3D cube and spiral.
Draw bezier, draw freehand lines, draw caligraphyc and tweak objects.
Fill bounded areas, gradients and sprites.
The special one. Important but with low frequency of use, thats why it's separated from the rest.
